snippet.title: (English) Teaser Movie 2022 - Wizardry Variants Daphne -
snippet.description:
Savor the risk.

Wizardry Variants Daphne carries on the lineage of the classic RPG series, Wizardry. The portal to the labyrinth of despair, where even destruction is pleasure, has opened once again.

▼official site
https://wizardry.info/daphne/en/  
▼Twitter
https://twitter.com/Wiz_Daphne_en

Title: Wizardry Variants Daphne 
Genre: 3D Dungeon RPG
Release Date:Early 2023
Supported Platforms: iOS/Android
Distribution: Worldwide (Japan and internationally)
